  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Members of the Tsukizuma clan are known to be incredibly lucky said to be the interference of the Moon Goddess in times of need, as a blessing to her descendents</p><p>Starting at 1st Level, you gain 2 Lunar Luck dice. Whenever you roll a d20, you can choose to store the result in your Lunar Luck Die, before knowing the consequence of the roll, and immediately reroll, taking the second result. For the next Minute, you can spend your Lunar Luck die in place of any roll of a d20 you would make, using the Number stored as if you had rolled it. If you would score a critical hit using this Feature, half the additional damage die. You gain additional Lunar Luck die at 7th, 11th and 15th level. You regain all your Lunar Luck die on a Short Rest, and all Lunar Luck die you have remaining are lost.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
